---
import SEOPage from '../../layouts/SEOPage.astro';

const site = 'https://getmizra.com';
const canonical = `${site}/use-case/lancio/`;

const articleLD = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": "Case Study: Lancio.fr — How Mizra Built a Custom Back-Office for a French Web Agency",
  "description": "How Lancio.fr industrialized its lead pipeline with a custom back-office built by Mizra in 48 hours: CRM, quotes, invoicing, and KPI dashboard.",
  "datePublished": "2026-03-23",
  "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Mizra", "url": site },
  "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Mizra", "url": site },
  "mainEntityOfPage": { "@type": "WebPage", "@id": canonical },
};

const breadcrumbLD = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": `${site}/` },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Use Cases", "item": `${site}/use-case/lancio/` },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Lancio.fr" },
  ],
};
---

<SEOPage
  title="Case Study: Lancio.fr — Custom Back-Office by Mizra"
  description="How Lancio.fr industrialized its lead pipeline with a custom back-office built by Mizra in 48h: CRM, quotes, invoicing, and KPI dashboard."
  canonical={canonical}
  jsonLd={[articleLD, breadcrumbLD]}
>

<div class="cx">
  <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb" style="direction:ltr;text-align:left;">
    <a href="/">Home</a><span>/</span><a href="/use-case/lancio/">Use Cases</a><span>/</span><span>Lancio.fr</span>
  </nav>
</div>

<article class="uc" style="direction:ltr;text-align:left;">
<div class="cx">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <header class="uc-hero">
    <span class="uc-tag">Case Study · Web Agency · France</span>
    <h1>How <i>Lancio.fr</i> industrialized its acquisition with a custom back-office</h1>
    <p class="uc-sub">From manual prospection to an automated pipeline: Lancio.fr now manages its leads, quotes and invoices from a single interface built by Mizra.</p>
  </header>

  <!-- METRICS -->
  <div class="uc-metrics rv">
    <div class="uc-metric">
      <div class="uc-metric-val">48h</div>
      <div class="uc-metric-lbl">Delivery time</div>
    </div>
    <div class="uc-metric">
      <div class="uc-metric-val">3×</div>
      <div class="uc-metric-lbl">Leads processed / week</div>
    </div>
    <div class="uc-metric">
      <div class="uc-metric-val">100%</div>
      <div class="uc-metric-lbl">Digitalized back-office</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CONTENT GRID -->
  <div class="uc-grid">
    <div class="uc-main">

      <!-- CONTEXTE -->
      <section class="uc-section rv">
        <div class="sl">Context</div>
        <h2>An agency scaling up — without the infrastructure</h2>
        <p>Lancio.fr is a French web agency specializing in website creation for small businesses and freelancers. With offers priced between €650 and €1,500, their prospect volume is high — but their internal organization hadn't kept up.</p>
        <p>Before working with Mizra, the Lancio team managed quotes in Excel, follow-ups manually by email, and had zero real-time visibility on their commercial pipeline.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- CHALLENGE / SOLUTION -->
      <section class="uc-section rv">
        <div class="sl">Challenge</div>
        <h2>Too many leads, not enough tools</h2>
        <div class="uc-twocol">
          <div class="uc-block uc-block-before">
            <div class="uc-block-title">Before Mizra</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Lead tracking on spreadsheets</li>
              <li>Quotes created manually</li>
              <li>No centralized invoicing</li>
              <li>Follow-ups forgotten or late</li>
              <li>Zero visibility on conversion rate</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="uc-block uc-block-after">
            <div class="uc-block-title">After Mizra</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Lightweight CRM built into the back-office</li>
              <li>One-click quote generation</li>
              <li>Numbered, exportable invoicing</li>
              <li>Live performance dashboard</li>
              <li>Everything centralized, accessible anywhere</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- BO HIGHLIGHT -->
      <section class="uc-section rv">
        <div class="sl">Solution</div>
        <h2>A back-office designed for agencies that prospect</h2>
        <p>Mizra delivered in 48 hours a complete back-office, connected to Supabase, with an admin interface designed for non-technical sales teams.</p>

        <div class="uc-bo">
          <h3>Lancio back-office modules</h3>
          <div class="uc-bo-grid">
            <div class="uc-bo-item">
              <span class="uc-bo-icon">📥</span>
              <div>
                <strong>CSV Lead Import</strong>
                <p>Bulk import from Lobstr or any scraping source</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="uc-bo-item">
              <span class="uc-bo-icon">🗂️</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Visual Pipeline</strong>
                <p>Statuses: New, Contacted, Quote Sent, Signed, Lost</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="uc-bo-item">
              <span class="uc-bo-icon">📄</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Quote Generation</strong>
                <p>Numbered quotes, auto-generated PDFs, email delivery</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="uc-bo-item">
              <span class="uc-bo-icon">💳</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Invoice Tracking</strong>
                <p>Invoices linked to quotes, CSV export, payment status</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="uc-bo-item">
              <span class="uc-bo-icon">📊</span>
              <div>
                <strong>KPI Dashboard</strong>
                <p>Monthly revenue, conversion rate, leads by source</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="uc-bo-item">
              <span class="uc-bo-icon">🔐</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Secure Access</strong>
                <p>Admin login, multi-user, securely hosted data</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- QUOTE -->
      <blockquote class="uc-quote rv">
        <p>"We had the offer, we had the clients — we were missing the infrastructure. Mizra delivered in 48h what we'd been putting off for months."</p>
        <cite>— Lancio.fr Team · Web Agency, France</cite>
      </blockquote>

      <!-- RESULTS -->
      <section class="uc-section rv">
        <div class="sl">Results</div>
        <h2>A pipeline finally under control</h2>
        <div class="uc-results">
          <div class="uc-result">
            <div class="uc-result-num">3×</div>
            <p>More leads processed per week thanks to automated CSV import</p>
          </div>
          <div class="uc-result">
            <div class="uc-result-num">€0</div>
            <p>SaaS subscription saved — everything is proprietary, no recurring fees</p>
          </div>
          <div class="uc-result">
            <div class="uc-result-num">48h</div>
            <p>Delivery time for the complete back-office, operational from day 2</p>
          </div>
          <div class="uc-result">
            <div class="uc-result-num">100%</div>
            <p>Quotes and invoices generated from the BO — spreadsheets are gone</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <p class="uc-footer-note">
        Case study in partnership with <a href="https://lancio.fr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lancio.fr</a> — French web agency specialized in small businesses & freelancers.
      </p>

    </div>

    <!-- SIDEBAR -->
    <aside class="uc-sidebar">
      <div class="uc-card">
        <h4>Client Profile</h4>
        <div class="uc-row"><span>Client</span><span>Lancio.fr</span></div>
        <div class="uc-row"><span>Sector</span><span>Web Agency</span></div>
        <div class="uc-row"><span>Country</span><span>France 🇫🇷</span></div>
        <div class="uc-row"><span>Delivery</span><span>48 hours</span></div>
        <div class="uc-row"><span>Type</span><span>Back-office + CRM</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="uc-card">
        <h4>Tech Stack</h4>
        <div class="uc-tags">
          <span class="uc-tag-item">Supabase</span>
          <span class="uc-tag-item">Next.js</span>
          <span class="uc-tag-item">Vercel</span>
          <span class="uc-tag-item">Brevo</span>
          <span class="uc-tag-item">CSV Import</span>
          <span class="uc-tag-item">PDF Auto</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="uc-card">
        <h4>Modules Delivered</h4>
        <div class="uc-row"><span>CRM Leads</span><span>✓</span></div>
        <div class="uc-row"><span>Quotes</span><span>✓</span></div>
        <div class="uc-row"><span>Invoicing</span><span>✓</span></div>
        <div class="uc-row"><span>Dashboard</span><span>✓</span></div>
        <div class="uc-row"><span>CSV Export</span><span>✓</span></div>
        <div class="uc-row"><span>Admin Auth</span><span>✓</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="uc-backlink">
        <div class="uc-backlink-label">Our Partner</div>
        <p>Lancio.fr is a French web agency that delivers professional websites for freelancers starting at €650.</p>
        <a href="https://lancio.fr" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-p btn-sm">Visit Lancio.fr →</a>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>

</div>
</article>

</SEOPage>
